{"tid":2412408,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"39年歷史 日資服飾店ICE FIRE說再見：香港分店陸續結業","createTime":"2021-02-18T04:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T04:28:11.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"524f6e5497397acfffe14e08449d20bd389e2777","tid":2412408,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"已經有39年歷史，以香港業務為中心的日資服飾店ICE FIRE，終於要為它的香港故事畫上句號。曾為香港引入日本品牌的它，以往是潮流指標的店鋪，而在近年網購、fast fashion等的因素下，它的名氣好像已有所減少。大家也有去過ICE FIRE嗎？<br />\n<br />\n日資連鎖零售商ICE FIRE，成立於1982年，主力出售日本與美國的潮流品牌服飾，其中包括：VAN、Luggage Label、SCHOTT、Champion、Dickies，其中SCENE的大字衣更是很多人的回憶。另一方面，他們會舉行工廈開倉，這也是每年的一大盛事。現時他們有荃灣、深水埗、旺角、尖沙咀、黃埔、灣仔的分店。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/ice-fire-hk-close/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Fice-fire-hk-close%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOiLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=2f96b6a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/ice-fire-hk-close/</a>"},{"pid":"380fcab29036ff4ddaba644b258292dd32df9f32","tid":2412408,"uid":50972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:24:10.000Z","msg":"佢而家一咪賣d 抄款打板款<br />\n攪到9唔搭8 仲要貴"},{"pid":"df9c4458e1eb4ee8b6c8d589adba146088d7a5d0","tid":2412408,"uid":18310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:27:25.000Z","msg":"果個價錢唔係開倉都唔會買啦"},{"pid":"d5f661cdf321cf3c3b85861122401082613dbef3","tid":2412408,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"又可以懷念打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}